-strickland\">Michael Strickland, Ph.D.</a></p>\n<ul>\n    <li>B.S., Environmental Science and Management, University of California-Davis, 2020</li>\n    <li>My hometown is San Francisco, California</li>\n</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-lg-4 pull-left-sm pull-right-lg clear-right-lg optional-content-wrapper\">\n\n\t</div>\n</div>"}
