uild</li> \n<li>ARCH 454/554: Vertical Studio -Design Build</li>\n<li>ARCH 461: Building Assemblies</li>\n<li>ARCH 556: Graduate Project</li>\n</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>"}
