 src=\"/-/media/UIdaho-Responsive/Images/caa/Programs/Art-and-Design/meet-our-people/people/lauren-mccleary.jpg?h=800&amp;la=en&amp;w=800&amp;hash=FA8F32DF49FC8870D9A3032A25465513EDCF1650\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Lauren McCleary\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\">\n\t\t</div>\n\n\n\n\t\t\t\t<p><a class=\"profile-link\" href=\"/caa/programs/art-design/our-people/lauren-mccleary\">View Full Profile <span class=\"icon-arrow-r\"></span></a></p>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-lg-8 person-info-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"profile-container summary\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Lauren moved from Colorado to the Palouse in 2007 and received her M.F.A. from Washington State University. She has previously worked for the U of I Prichard Art Gallery as the Education Outreach Coordinator and loves getting to know the Moscow community through arts programming. For over a decade, she has been developing her skills as a cut paper and collage artist. Her process allows her to turn mental and emotional clutter and chaos into simple cuts of paper.</p>\n<h4>Areas of Focus</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>K-12 Arts Education</li>\n    <li>Museum and Gallery Education</li>\n    <li>Community Engagement</li>\n</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"profile-container education\">\n            <p><a href=\"/caa\">College of Art and Architecture</a></p>\n\n            <p><a href=\"/caa/programs/art-design\">Art and Design</a></p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"profile-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n<li>B.F.A., Emphasis in Drawing, Metropolitan State University of Denver, 2007</li><li>\n\nK-12 Art Education Licensure, Metropolitan University of Denver, 2007</li><li>\n\nM.F.A., Emphasis in Drawing, Washington State University, 2009</li>\n</ul>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-lg-4 pull-left-sm pull-right-lg clear-right-lg optional-content-wrapper\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"links profile-container-optional-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4>Courses Taught</h4>\n\t\t\t\t